07:25.320 --> 07:27.026
Papa would have enjoyed your speech.

07:27.200 --> 07:29.304
Your father would have graced the House

07:29.480 --> 07:32.426
with more dignity
and less notoriety than I can muster.

07:34.520 --> 07:36.499
A toast, then.

07:37.840 --> 07:40.502
- To Francis Poldark!
- And his son.

07:43.000 --> 07:44.979
(Woman laughs nearby)

07:49.720 --> 07:51.904
Fame has its rewards.

07:54.080 --> 07:56.105
ROSS: May I offer you some refreshment?

07:59.840 --> 08:03.105
