The drawbacks of being a Cornish MP
who actually lives in Cornwall.

09:00.680 --> 09:03.342
One cannot simply dash home
when the need arises.

09:03.520 --> 09:05.579
- I take it the need has arisen?
- Yes.

09:06.680 --> 09:11.800
